des:
Alsmai smart offers the most comprehensive voice-controlled smart home experience with Alexa. Control your home oven and other devices hands free.

Here’s a step by step guide:
(1). Download our "Alsmai smart" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and register a new account (or login if you’re already registered);
(3). Turn on Alsmai smart devices and connect them with “Alsmai smart” app;
(4). IMPORTANT: You can rename the devices with Alsmai smart App. So if you rename a smart bulb “Home oven”, then Echo will get that same name after discovered the devices in Step 9;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store, and connect Echo with "Alexa" app;
(6). Search the Alexa Skills directory for "Alsmai smart";
(7). Click Enable skill of "Alsmai smart", then input your account username, password and region on the linking page;
(8). Talk to Echo "“Alexa,discover devices.”. Wait till Echo says "Discover is completed";
(9). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo to control your devices.

Here are the voice commands Alsmai smart has:

Oven:
pause on oven
restart on oven
stop on oven
turn on child lock on oven
turn off light on oven
defrost on oven

Range hood
turn on child lock on range hood
turn off light on range hood
turn off fan on range hood

set the fan speed on the range hood to two
set the range hood to fifty percent
